description:
Ice destroyed The Rock. The Rock came in confident that she would do well. Wrestling her brothers all those years had to count for something, right? The Rock is also in great shape and very strong, but Ice was too much for her in every category.
Lately we've been trying to hide who wins the match, but here it is obvious. In this update you will find back breakers, grapevines, camel clutches, painful submissions and total sexual humiliation during the match by the loser. A great one-sided match. During Rd 4 The Rock said she squirts when she comes, so why not.
title: Janay and Angela Stone
